  "texts": [
    "You'll see that they are increasing by a constant amount each time.",
    "This indicates that this is an arithmetic series.",
    "Here, the differences are increasing by 6 each time (12 -6 = 6, 14 -8 = 6).",
    "Based on this pattern, we can predict that the difference between 7 and the missing number should be 6 + 2 = 8.",
    "So, the missing number should be 7 + 8 = 15."
  ],
